steps.name: Click on the 'Companies' button from the sidebar menu
Click on the 'Clients' tab from the 'Companies' page
Click on the client name from the table
Click on the 'Client information' tab from the company landing page
Click on the 'Schedule' sub tab from the company landing page
Click on the 'Action' button from the 'Schedules' sub tab
Click on the 'Next' button on the 'Create schedule' modal
Enter schedule template name into the 'Search' input field
Select and click on the first schedule in the list
